<div class='col-sm-10 col-sm-offset-1' style="margin-top: 16px;">
  <h4 class="usage-checklist__title">{{t "Core Words" key="core_words"}}</h4>
  <ul class="usage-checklist">
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "Core words are high-frequency, everyday words with multiple meanings. They help communicators participate across the whole day—not just in one or two situations." key="core_1"}}</li>
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "Core words let people build their own sentences instead of relying on a long list of pre-made phrases." key="core_2"}}</li>
    <li class="usage-checklist__item">{{t "Choose a vocabulary set with enough core words for the communicator to grow into—and plan with the end in mind." key="core_3"}}</li>
  </ul>
